channel.title: Assignment #0: Hello, World! :: Java Web Development
channel.description: The purpose of this initial assignment is to familiarize yourself with the process of running the autograding tests with Github Actions and submitting your work. Even if you are familiar with GitHub Actions, this assignment will contain several new items that are specific to working with Java assignments.
